data.meta_description: LCpl. James, 25, of Jacksonville, NC, formerly of Lansing, MI.  passed away on Tuesday, March 26, 2019.  James was a graduate of Lansing Eastern High School and was currently serving in the U.S. Marine Corps with the 8th Communications Battalion stationed at Camp Lejeune, NC.  James was also a very talented tattoo...
